        {
            "_id": "Y2A2TDZs3XxPwNrE",
            "img": "systems/pf2e/icons/actions/OneAction.webp",
            "name": "Highly Confusing Scheme",
            "sort": 1100000,
            "system": {
                "actionType": {
                    "value": "action"
                },
                "actions": {
                    "value": 1
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The durtik provides so much detail about their confusing scheme that it overwhelms their target. The durtik attempts a Deception check to [[/act feint]] against an opponent up to 30 feet away. If they succeed, the @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Off-Guard] penalty applies when the durtik or any construct it controls with Mechanized Animus makes a melee or ranged Strike.</p>"
                },
                "publication": {
                    "license": "OGL",
                    "remaster": false,
                    "title": ""
                },
                "rules": [],
                "slug": null,
                "traits": {
                    "value": [
                        "auditory",
                        "concentrate",
                        "linguistic",
                        "mental"
                    ]
                }
            },
            "type": "action"
        },
        {
            "_id": "C4Y53V3IuGd3pBho",
            "img": "systems/pf2e/icons/actions/TwoActions.webp",
            "name": "Mechanized Animus",
            "sort": 1200000,
            "system": {
                "actionType": {
                    "value": "action"
                },
                "actions": {
                    "value": 2
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The durtik channels their antipathy and disdain for others into a construct within 60 feet, seizing control or making it come to life. The durtik attempts a @Check[crafting|against:will|options:inflicts:stupefied,inflicts:stunned] check against the construct's Will DC or its controller's (if any) Will DC, whichever is higher. The durtik can't use Mechanized Animus again for [[/gmr 1d4 #Recharge Mechanized Animus]]{1d4 rounds}.</p><hr /><p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The construct immediately takes two basic actions of the durtik's choosing and is then @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Stunned]{Stunned 2}.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The construct immediately takes one basic action of the durtik's choosing and is then @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Stunned]{Stunned 1}.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The destructive antipathy rebounds, and the durtik is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Stupefied]{Stupefied 2} for 1 minute.</p>"
                },
                "publication": {
                    "license": "OGL",
                    "remaster": false,
                    "title": ""
                },
                "rules": [],
                "slug": null,
                "traits": {
                    "value": [
                        "concentrate",
                        "incapacitation",
                        "magical"
                    ]
                }
            },
            "type": "action"
        },
